Package: erlang-estap
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, erlang-base
Description: test framework for Erlang
 estap is a simple test framework for Erlang, designed to be run under
 `prove', Test::Harness or similar tools.

